title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - What's new in the marketplace - Week 42
description:
In this video we will look at the latest additions to the MSFS 2020 marketplace this week. This week is a week with a lot of new items: mainly a lot of night enhancements and a small amount of new airports, aircrafts, helicopters as well as some mission packs and of course livery packs.  

Please provide feedback using the comment box below as I have been experimenting a lot to make the audio/voice quality better. If you have suggestions feel free to provide them so I can enhance the audio quality.
